citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:50- 1:35
PM on 02-OCT-18.
Inspector arrived at 12:50 pm knocked on door, called out for the licensee, honked horn and call listed number and
left message.
